      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POWER VALLEY (2) flew the lids with a slick early split last time and went on to clock 19.87 as a strongly fancied winner over 350m at this track. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Sure to prove hard to beat. AUSSIE BONUS (1) was always well back but did hit the line strongly late to finish 5th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (20.74) at this track. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Can do much better this time. PATIENT VICKY (5) is a promising type who notched her 4th career success when too good (23.07) at The Gardens last time. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. RUSHFORTH BAZ (8) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
